WEBVTT

00:02.969 --> 00:05.170
(MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS)

00:06.570 --> 00:07.569
Someone wants your book?

00:07.570 --> 00:10.137
They want me to go down to
Sydney to meet with them.

00:10.637 --> 00:11.736
Give me a kiss.

00:11.737 --> 00:12.803
I said no!

00:12.804 --> 00:14.403
No one says no to me.

00:14.404 --> 00:15.936
(GASPS)

00:17.537 --> 00:19.101
He won't get away with this.

00:19.102 --> 00:23.535
They'll call you a tramp and
ruin your brother's career.

00:23.536 --> 00:25.769
Is Georgie mine?

00:25.770 --> 00:28.802
Of course Georgie is yours!
He's our little boy!

00:28.803 --> 00:30.302
(VOICE BREAKING) Our baby didn't live.

00:31.336 --> 00:33.301
I couldn't tell him.

00:33.303 --> 00:35.303
(MUSIC CONTINUES)

00:36.437 --> 00:38.102
Livvy, wait! Wait!

00:38.103 --> 00:40.470
- Let me explain.
- Explain what?

00:41.437 --> 00:42.536
OLIVIA: What is this?

00:42.537 --> 00:44.070
I got a little carried away.

00:48.737 --> 00:51.503
We're going on an adventure, aren't we?

00:51.504 --> 00:52.935
Where's my son?

00:52.936 --> 00:56.669
ELIZABETH: A marriage of
convenience is easy to say.

00:56.670 --> 00:58.336
It's not always easy to live.

00:58.337 --> 00:59.436
I hope you're very certain

00:59.437 --> 01:01.302
that she doesn't expect you to love her.

01:01.303 --> 01:02.136
No, René!

01:02.137 --> 01:04.370
<i>Mon amour! Je suis là.</i>

01:06.771 --> 01:08.202
Why are you here?

01:08.203 --> 01:09.536
To pay my respects.

01:09.537 --> 01:10.436
Liar!

01:10.437 --> 01:13.436
The fact is, to have a
successful political career,

01:13.437 --> 01:15.236
I need someone by my side.

01:15.237 --> 01:18.202
Whatever was between us,
George, you're a married man.

01:18.203 --> 01:20.736
- Nothing else matters.
- I'm equally unavailable.

01:20.737 --> 01:22.603
We will be together, Sarah.

01:22.604 --> 01:23.569
I promise you.

01:23.570 --> 01:24.604
Oh.

01:25.771 --> 01:27.003
(GRUNTS)

01:29.003 --> 01:32.536
GEORGE: <i>To Sarah Nordmann, I
give, devise, and bequeath</i>

01:32.537 --> 01:36.303
<i>finances held in trust on
behalf of our unborn child.</i>

